    {
      "id": "6123cf49aff09e0000a21e45",
      "text": "[https://hbr.org/2017/07/being-the-boss-in-brussels-boston-and-beijing To Lead Across Cultures, Focus on Hierarchy and Decision Making]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
